fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 rose 36.15 points or 0.18% to settle at 19,611.05. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, declined 1.27% to 10.68. HDFC Bank, ICICI Bank and Axis Bank were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The September 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 28 September 2023.
